{"tid":1963674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"14世紀的「黑死病」源自中國","createTime":"2020-04-08T09:55:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T12:25:05.000Z","uid":172184,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0567ea263c29897a87ec9846168499ebf0e1ee24","tid":1963674,"uid":172184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T09:55:05.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">14世紀的「黑死病」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n14世紀在歐洲肆虐的鼠疫，一旦感染便會在2到7日內出現發燒症狀，皮膚上浮現紫黑色的斑點和腫塊，因而被稱為「黑死病」。加拿大籍歷史學家威廉&middot;哈代&middot;麥克尼爾稱，侵略了<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">支那</span></strong>雲南省的蒙古軍將鼠疫桿菌的媒介&mdash;&mdash;跳蚤與受感染的老鼠帶到了中世紀的歐洲，因而引起了「黑死病」的大流行。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">黑死病在歐洲的傳播</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鼠疫於1320年至1330年左右在<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中國</span></strong>大肆流行，剛剛傳播到歐州時也在馬穆魯克王朝等伊斯蘭世界中肆虐。蒙古帝國打通歐亞大陸、商業貿易逐漸繁盛之後，這種疾病於14世紀擴散到了整個歐洲。<br />\n<br />\n汁：<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%82%B3%E6%9F%93%E7%97%85%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E5%2582%25B3%25E6%259F%2593%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E5%258F%25B2&d=LgTIxyFtuo0acoW68XVTBaVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=09512e37\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%82%B3%E6%9F%93%E7%97%85%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2</a>"},{"pid":"9aa104f5327cf925ff5b46a1188220c3e9e382eb","tid":1963674,"uid":157799,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T09:55:48.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，好怕大家忘記了，可唔可以入嚟幫手推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n［5個月］［整合］大家記唔記得今日係咩日子<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1963297\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1963297</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/08/171441_9b725230f319dbfd347dc84fa175d02e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F08%2F171441_9b725230f319dbfd347dc84fa175d02e.png&h=bb404f5b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"057b7b960bc5d1237fb397a206b4c2268d1c834a","tid":1963674,"uid":172184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9aa104f5327cf925ff5b46a1188220c3e9e382eb","tid":1963674,"uid":157799,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T09:55:48.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，好怕大家忘記了，可唔可以入嚟幫手推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n［5個月］［整合］大家記唔記得今日係咩日子<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1963297\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1963297</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/08/171441_9b725230f319dbfd347dc84fa175d02e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F08%2F171441_9b725230f319dbfd347dc84fa175d02e.png&h=bb404f5b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T09:56:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2cb7caab3cd881c57c2081820dfb4dbc8bc6f207","tid":1963674,"uid":65638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T10:07:30.000Z","msg":"支那真係累人累物"},{"pid":"571757c62c60df299daf164cae9b67982670b74d","tid":1963674,"uid":125542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T10:09:05.000Z","msg":"中共又再篡改歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8af8a93caf5136528c04c31a9ad474dba43d777","tid":1963674,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T10:41:15.000Z","msg":"成吉思汗帶來病毒攻入歐洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17fe576c3c917545a3aab98f975bd09109a19c14","tid":1963674,"uid":302250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:25:05.000Z","msg":"至正四年（1344年），中國淮河流域爆發黑死病（《明史》卷一，太祖本紀，「至正四年，旱蝗，大飢疫。太祖時年十七，父母兄相繼歿，貧不克葬。」），河北商人再沿「絲路」將之傳到印度、中亞、波斯、敘利亞、美索不達米亞等地。同時期蒙古金帳汗國在攻打克里米亞的卡法城市時，將染疫屍體用投石機投入城中，由此散佈病毒至歐洲各處。造成1347年歐洲大流行，大文豪薄伽丘的《十日談》即是以這場瘟疫為故事背景，描寫浩劫下的人性。至正十九年（1359年）春夏，莒州沂水、日照二縣和廣東南雄路大疫。"}]}